<p style="text-align:left;font-size:1.3em;padding-left:3px;font-family:'Trebuchet MS',Arial,Helvetica,Verdana,sans-serif;"> MethodBox is brought to you by a team from the <a href = "http://www.manchester.ac.uk">University of Manchester</a> in the UK, led by Principle Investigators <a href="http://www.manchester.ac.uk/research/carole.a.goble/">Carole Goble</a>, <a href="http://www.manchester.ac.uk/research/Buchan/">Iain Buchan</a> and <a href="http://www.manchester.ac.uk/research/angela.dale/">Angela Dale</a>.
