<p style="text-align:left;font-size:1.3em;padding-left:3px;font-family:'Trebuchet MS',Arial,Helvetica,Verdana,sans-serif;">MethodBox is part of the Obesity eLab project funded by the <a href="http://www.esrc.ac.uk">Economic and Social Research Council</a> and supported by <a href="http://www.digitalsocialresearch.net/wordpress/">Digital Social Research</a>.</p>
<p style="text-align:left;font-size:1.3em;padding-left:3px;font-family:'Trebuchet MS',Arial,Helvetica,Verdana,sans-serif;">The MethodBox software is developed by the <a href="http://www.mygrid.org.uk">myGrid</a> team and is designed by a joint team from <a href="http://www.mygrid.org.uk">myGrid</a>, the <a href="https://www.nibhi.org.uk/">North West Institute for BioHealth Informatics</a> and the <a href="http://www.ccsr.ac.uk">Cathie Marsh Centre for Census and Survey Research</a>.</p>
